<h3>Introduction</h3>
<p>
A palindrome is a word, phrase, number, or other sequence of units that may be read the same way in either direction, 
with general allowances for adjustments to punctuation and word dividers.
<br/><br/>
The score will be half of the length of palindrome string (puntuatation and word dividers is not included), the score will be round up to a integer.
<br/><br/>
Only registered member can be shown in the rank list. 
</p>
